CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1956, pg. A17, reads: "Alpha Queen - Lovely Lee Brun [LeeBrun] Johnson was crowned the queen of Alpha Phi Alpha last Friday at the handsome ball given at Gateway Plaza. Here she is shown with lovely members of her court.  Left and clockwise: Gwendolyn L. Poinsette, Carrie Alston, Eleanor Morrison, the queen, Barbara Jean Peace, Alpha Phi Alpha's 1956 sweetheart; Phyllis Ball and Eleanor Coleman. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Phi Alpha queen and her court, from left: Gwendolyn L. Poinsette, Carrie Alston, Eleanor Morrison, queen LeeBrun Johnson, Barbara Jean Peace, Phyllis Ball, and Eleanor Coleman, posed in Gateway Plaza for Alpha Phi Alpha ball
